# Replace Text2Image Agent: Old Replicate → V2 Pollinations.AI

## Background

The current `text2image.py` agent uses **Replicate's SDXL model** which requires a paid API key (`REPLICATE_API_TOKEN`). The new v2 implementation uses **Pollinations.AI** which is **completely free** — no API key, no signup, no cost.

### Key Differences

| Aspect | Old (Replicate) | New (Pollinations.AI) |
|--------|----------------|----------------------|
| API Key Required | ✅ Yes (`REPLICATE_API_TOKEN`) | ❌ No |
| Cost | 💰 Paid | 🆓 Free |
| Models | SDXL only | FLUX, FLUX-Realism, Turbo, 3D, Anime, Dark |
| Image sizes | Fixed 1024×1024 | 512–1280 configurable |
| Dependencies | `replicate` package | `requests`, `Pillow` (already present) |

---

## User Review Required

> [!IMPORTANT]
> The old agent returned **image URLs from Replicate** (temporary URLs that expire). The new agent will generate images via Pollinations.AI and **save them to disk** in `outputs/images/`, returning the file path. The backend and frontend will be updated to handle both URL and file-path results seamlessly.

> [!IMPORTANT]
> The `replicate` Python package and `REPLICATE_API_TOKEN` environment variable will no longer be needed after this change. The `utils/image_client.py` file (Replicate client) will be **removed** since no other agent uses it.

---

## Proposed Changes

### Agent Layer

#### [DELETE] [text2image.py](file:///c:/Users/CSE/Desktop/xtra/xtra/agents/text2image.py)
- Remove the old Replicate-based text2image agent entirely.

#### [NEW] [text2image_v2.py](file:///c:/Users/CSE/Desktop/xtra/xtra/agents/text2image_v2.py)
- New agent class `Text2ImageV2Agent` following the same patterns as `ImageAnalysisAgent` and `SummarizerAgent`:
  - Class-based with `__init__`, `generate_image()`, `close()`, context manager support
  - Uses Pollinations.AI API (free, no key required)
  - `generate_image(prompt: str) → dict` returning `{"status": "success", "image_path": "...", "message": "..."}`
  - Saves images to `outputs/images/` with unique timestamped filenames
  - Supports configurable model, width, height, seed, and enhance parameters
  - Comprehensive error handling and logging
  - Always enabled (no API key check needed)

---

### Utility Layer

#### [DELETE] [image_client.py](file:///c:/Users/CSE/Desktop/xtra/xtra/utils/image_client.py)
- Remove the Replicate API client — it is only used by the old `text2image.py` agent.

---

### Workflow Layer

#### [MODIFY] [workflow.py](file:///c:/Users/CSE/Desktop/xtra/xtra/graph/workflow.py)
- **Import**: Replace `from agents.text2image import Text2ImageAgent` → `from agents.text2image_v2 import Text2ImageV2Agent`
- **`create_workflow()`**: Replace `Text2ImageAgent(config)` → `Text2ImageV2Agent()` (no config needed — no API key)
- **`node_text_to_image()`**: Update to handle the new dict response format `{"status": ..., "image_path": ..., "image_url": ...}`
- **`build_workflow()`**: Replace initialization — no more disabled/fallback state needed since v2 is always available
- No changes to routing logic — `TaskType.IMAGE_GENERATION` remains the same

---

### Backend Layer

#### [MODIFY] [backend.py](file:///c:/Users/CSE/Desktop/xtra/xtra/backend.py)
- **`process_and_download()`**: Update to handle `image_path` results alongside `image_url`. Serve local files via `StaticFiles` or return path in JSON.
- Mount `/outputs` as a static file directory for serving generated images.

---

### Config Layer

#### [MODIFY] [config.py](file:///c:/Users/CSE/Desktop/xtra/xtra/config.py)
- Remove `replicate_api_token` property and its validation/logging (lines 98, 115–126)
- Remove the Replicate-related comments from the docstring

#### [MODIFY] [.env](file:///c:/Users/CSE/Desktop/xtra/xtra/.env)
- Remove the `REPLICATE_API_TOKEN` line

---

### Requirements

#### [MODIFY] [requirements.txt](file:///c:/Users/CSE/Desktop/xtra/xtra/requirements.txt)
- **Remove**: `replicate==1.0.7`
- **Keep**: `requests`, `Pillow` (already present, needed by v2)
